This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and specifically focuses on using large language models for paraphrasing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves optimization techniques, which could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval techniques, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
